data.description: GREAT HOME TO RAISE YOUR FAMILY! This spacious 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom in Kissimmee's Doral Pointe Neighborhood has a Great Split Bedroom Layout. The house offers an Open Floorplan from the Kitchen to Living/Dining Area. The kitchen has modernized large wood cabinets with crown molding and Stainless Steel Appliances, along with recessed lighting. Water Filtration System in the House. Ceramic Tile Flooring in the Kitchen and Foyer. Newly added High-grade Vinyl Laminate Fooring throughout the house & bedrooms. Master Bedroom with walk-in Closet. Master Bathroom has Roman Tub & separate Shower Stall and Dual Sink Vanity. 3 Other Bedrooms are Ideal for your little ones room and/or Home Office. Large Laundry Room with Washer & Dryer and built-in pantry shelving. Solar Panel System, only 2 years old, installed on the roof for replacement of Electricity Demands. Totally reduced Electric Bill to almost nothing. Completely Fenced-in Backyard with Storage Shed and large enough for your little ones & pets to run around. Sprinkler System with Water Reclamation. Only 10 Minutes from great Shopping Centers & Restaurants.
